    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">1. AI-assisted workflow: Antigravity + Codex + Claude Code</h2>
        <p>In this workflow, AI acts as an engineering pair-programmer. The human sets priorities and approves output. AI helps with code edits, refactoring, translation, styling fixes, and implementation speed.</p>
        <p class="mb-0">In plain terms: AI does not magically generate the final website alone. It accelerates technical steps while the developer remains responsible for decisions and quality.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

